      <section class="about" id="about">
        <h2 class="section__title">about me</h2>

        <div class="about__wrapper">

          <img src="./dist/img/about_me.jpg" alt="" class="about__picture " data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="about__info">
            <h3 class="about__info-h3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">
              Hi! My name is Marcin
            </h3>
            <p class="about__info-p" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="350">
              I'm Accountant, Finance Controller and occasionally a Front End Developer
            </p>
            <p class="about__info-p" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="450">Privately - I am a very positive person,
              open to the world. I love to travel,
              sports (especially
              volleyball and skiing) and new technologies.</p>
            <p class="about__info-p" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="550">In my free time, I like to learn new things
              - that's how my adventure with
              programming began.
              Tried Python, Java, Visual Basic but felt in love with Front End Developing.</p>
            <p class="about__info-p" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="650">On this page you will find information
              about my experience and the courses I have
              taken.</p>
            <p class="about__info-p" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="750">Fell free to contact me anytime!</p>
          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

      <section class="experience" id="experience">

        <h2 class="section__title">experience</h2>

        <div class="accordion">
          <div class="accordion__item">

            <div class="accordion__item-title">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
              <p>McKinsey & Company</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="accordion__item-info">
              <li class="accordion__item-info-li">Managing clients budgets and ensuring the accurate costs allocations
                in financial system
              </li>
              <li class="accordion__item-info-li">Monitoring the time spent on the projects as well as other project
                related costs (travel,
                accommodation etc.)</li>
              <li class="accordion__item-info-li">Verifying whether expenses stay in line with the clients agreements
                and firm guidelines</li>
              <li class="accordion__item-info-li">Adressing inconsistencies to the partners and senior partners and
                proposing for solutions
              </li>
              <li class="accordion__item-info-li">Building long term relationships with stakeholders and act as an
                expert helping consultants
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

    </div>
